 0  |        |   Q    |   A    | extra   | SPACE  |   F1   |        | HOME   |
    |   `    |        |        | shift   |        |        |  SHIFT |        |
----|--------|--------|--------|---------|--------|--------|--------|--------|
    |   !    |        |        |         | BACK-  |        |  RIGHT |        |
 1  |        |   W    |   S    |    Z    | SPACE  |   F2   |        | END    |
    |   1    |        |        |         |        |        |  SHIFT |        |
----|--------|--------|--------|---------|--------|--------|--------|--------|
    |   \@    |        |        |         |        |        |  CAPS  | CDTV   |
 2  |        |   E    |   D    |    X    |  TAB   |   F3   |        |        |
    |   2    |        |        |         |        |        |  LOCK  | STOP   |
----|--------|--------|--------|---------|--------|--------|--------|--------|
    |   #    |        |        |         |  NP    |        |        | CDTV   |
 3  |        |   R    |   F    |    C    |        |   F4   |  CTRL  | PLAY/  |
    |   3    |        |        |         | ENTER  |        |        | PAUSE  |
----|--------|--------|--------|---------|--------|--------|--------|--------|
    |   $    |        |        |         |        |        |  LEFT  | CDTV   |
 4  |        |   T    |   G    |    V    | RETURN |   F5   |        |        |
    |   4    |        |        |         |        |        |  ALT   | PREV   |
----|--------|--------|--------|---------|--------|--------|--------|--------|
    |   %    |        |        |         |        |        |  RIGHT | CDTV   |
 5  |        |   Y    |   H    |    B    |  ESC   |   F6   |        |        |
    |   5    |        |        |         |        |        |  ALT   | NEXT   |
----|--------|--------|--------|---------|--------|--------|--------|--------|
    |   ^    |        |        |         |        |        |  LEFT  | CDTV   |
 6  |        |   U    |   J    |    N    |  DEL   |   F7   |        |        |
    |   6    |        |        |         |        |        |  AMIGA | REW    |
